headline: Booking Holdings to Webcast Third Quarter 2025 Financial Results on October 28
summary: Booking Holdings (NASDAQ: BKNG) announced today that it intends to hold a conference call to discuss its third quarter 2025 financial results on Tuesday, October 28 at 4:30 p.m. ET. The event will be webcast at ir.bookingholdings.com and the audio will be available for replay on the website for seven days thereafter.

headline: 2 S&P 500 Stocks with Competitive Advantages and 1 Facing Headwinds
summary: The S&P 500 (^GSPC) is home to the biggest and most well-known companies in the market, making it a go-to index for investors seeking stability. But not all large-cap stocks are created equal - some are struggling with slowing growth, declining margins, or increased competition.
